        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Stopping the Fraudulent Sales of Firearms Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes it unlawful to import, manufacture, or sell a firearm or ammunition by fraudulent means (e.g., false representations). Further, it makes it unlawful to transmit a wire, radio, or television communication in interstate or foreign commerce related to such a fraudulent importation, manufacture, or sale.</p> <p>A violator is subject to criminal penalties&#8212;a fine, a prison term of up to five years, or both.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
